'''Frank Newsbaum''' came into the hospital after being stabbed by his girlfriend's father.

==History==
Frank was attacked by his girlfriend's dad, [[Don (Invasion)|Don]]. Don didn't like that Frank was dating his much-younger daughter, [[Jeanie]]. The stab wounds were mostly superficial, but he was taken to the ER for treatment.

When Jeanie arrived in the ER, Don attacked him again, but [[Jackson Avery]] tackled him before he could do any damage.

Frank developed a pseudoaneurysm and was taken into angio to confirm before having surgery.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
He is dating [[Jeanie]], a much younger woman who used to babysit his kids.

===Familial===
He has at least two kids, whom his girlfriend used to babysit.

==Notes and Trivia==
*He was 42 at the time of his hospitalization.
